thread.title: BRIEF-Telenet And Nethys Sign Partnership To Deliver Voomobile Offering

author: Reuters Editorial
title: BRIEF-Telenet And Nethys Sign Partnership To Deliver Voomobile Offering
text:
Feb 6 (Reuters) - Telenet Group Holding Nv:
* NETHYS AND TELENET SIGN MAJOR PARTNERSHIP DEAL TO DELIVER THE VOOMOBILE OFFERING
* SIGNING A 5-YEAR AGREEMENT WITH NETHYS * ‍CONTRACT EXTENDS COLLABORATION BETWEEN TWO COMPANIES UNTIL 31 DECEMBER 2023​
* ‍VOOMOBILE CUSTOMERS WILL BE TRANSFERRED TO TELENET NETWORK DURING COURSE OF 2018​
* NEW PARTNERSHIP OPERATED ACROSS TELENET NETWORK, INSTEAD OF ORANGE NETWORK Source text for Eikon: Further company coverage: (Gdynia Newsroom)
